46
00:01:54,042 --> 00:01:55,251
Kenapa mereka gagal?

47
00:01:55,835 --> 00:01:57,420
Apa karena ekonomi sulit?

48
00:01:57,796 --> 00:01:58,755
Bukan karena itu.

49
